gawa
yekONasi roga samayare byakwimAne pracalYiwa aByAsagudZiku pAlYana karibe, yaxi semAnafkara banXuparijana ehi aByAsagudZiku guruwbapUrNFa mane karibe, semAne biSeRa BAbare pracalYiwa aByAsa o bipaxasafkulYa janasAXAraNafka prawi maXya sambexanaSIlYa Wibe, semAnafkara roganiyanwraNajaniwa jFAnakOSalYa maXya yaWeRta parimANare Wiba ebaM semAne ehi aByAsagudZiku nije pAlYana karuWibe.
yaxi seWi pAiz bAswaba BiwwiBUmi Wiba, wAhA sahiwa samanbiwa byabasWA kAryakArI hoiWiba, ebaM pracalYiwa aByAsagudZiku bikaSiwa karibA pAiz aXiniyama o niyamAbalYIra praswAbanA maXya hoiWiba.
bisisira kRewra bikaSiwa hebA pare ehA sAmAjika, pAripArSbika XAraNAku yaWeRta guruwba praxAna karuCi. waWA ehA byakwigawa aByAsagudZiku maXya sama parimANare bqxXi karuCi. weNu ehi pariprekRIre esabisisi bisisi wulYanAre aXika grahaNIya heuCi.
biwAnwi
kAraka
poRtaramAnafkare byafga o Baya mAXyamare janasAXAraNafkara xqRti AkarRaNa karAyAe.
praBAbara ehi cAroti swarare eBalYi upAxAna sabu rahiCi yAhA aByAsaku sakArAwmaka nakArAwmaka BAbare praBAbiwa karuCi. bisisira PalYapraxa upayoga hiz biBinna bArwwA, kAryyakramaku bikaSiwa karibA pAiz sAmAjika pAripArSbika namunAra prawyeka swaraku praBAbiwa karibA sahiwa subiXA praxAnakArIfku baDZAibA, prawibanXakagudiku hatAibA pAiz eka bAswaba lakRya XAraNa karibA AbaSyaka. yaxio ehA cihnata karibA guruwbapUrNFa hoipAre xaWApi gotie safgaTana pakRare cAroti swarare paricAlYanA karibA awyanwa kaRtasAXya byApAra. yehewu ehA kAryyakArI karibA pAiz aneka samayare Binna XaraNara kAryya xakRawA, kOSalYa o ABimuKya AbaSyaka.

